cs.CL, cs.LG, cs.AI, cs.CV, cs.IR 

This paper deals with natural language processing tasks, specifically relation extraction, and proposes a novel convolutional neural network with residual learning. Therefore, the most likely category is cs.CL (Computation and Language). The paper also involves deep learning techniques, which makes cs.LG (Machine Learning) another likely category. Additionally, the paper deals with artificial intelligence and computer vision tasks, which makes cs.AI and cs.CV possible categories. Finally, the paper involves information retrieval tasks, which makes cs.IR a possible category as well.
